---
title: Vietnamese Chicken Ca-ri with Mushrooms and Brown Rice
description: Curry can seem like a daunting dish to make at home, especially when you’re in a hurry. But with this recipe, you’ll have time and flavour on your side! When Mimi was creating this recipe, she received a surprise visit from the Brownlee brothers, who tasted and critiqued it with the culinary team. They even suggested a few tweaks which she applied! If it gets gold from Olympic athletes, we’re sure you’ll love it too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vietnamese-chicken-ca-ri-wk41-f64a47b4-3f089adb.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/vietnamese-chicken-ca-ri-wk41-5995782da1e1ea0f860e6b82-a92c8fc4.pdf
